The paper presents a neural approach to topic modeling, which involves training parameterizable distributions over topics using backpropagation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
